# Semgrep ignore patterns for Euxis project
# https://semgrep.dev/docs/ignoring-files/

# Test files - different security standards
**/test/**
**/tests/**
**/*_test.py
**/test_*.py
**/conftest.py

# Build and dependency directories
**/build/**
**/dist/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/node_modules/**
**/.pytest_cache/**
**/coverage_html/**

# Virtual environments
**/venv/**
**/.venv/**
**/env/**

# IDE and editor files
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~

# Temporary files
**/tmp/**
**/temp/**
**/*.tmp
**/*.log
**/*.bak

# Generated documentation
**/docs/_build/**
**/site/**

# Configuration files with acceptable patterns
**/.github/workflows/*.yml
**/pyproject.toml
**/package.json
**/tsconfig.json

# Data and runtime directories
**/euxis-runtime/**
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.jsonl

# Cryptographic test vectors and examples (acceptable in context)
**/euxis-crypto-**/examples/**
**/test-vectors/**

# Third-party code
**/vendor/**
**/third-party/**

# Specific files with known acceptable security patterns
euxis-core/lib/providers.sh
bin/lib/*.sh